description: GuardiansOfTheRealm collection is designed by Orojan Peter. GuardiansOfTheRealm collection will have 100pcs + 10pcs special for our Founders Coin owners. GuardiansOfTheRealm collection will have 10 types of humanoid creatures. Every creature will have 10 different iterations, different accessories, and complex designs. Each type of creature will start with basic characteristics and advance to more complex ones.
